No matter how many goals you reach it won't make you happy. Life isn't  just about reaching goals it's about reaching peace, because you'll just be endlessly chasing accolades your whole life. If I finally get a car I'll be happy, when I get my dream job I'll be good, when I make a million a year I'll be at peace. Peace isn't at the end of any goal you reach. Trust me. It's here in the now just waiting for you to acknowledge it all along. #thecrookedmile
